item.title: Dj Arity WWDMN - 04-12-2012
item.description:
Hi Everyone,

It's been sometime since the last post. I have been really busy with life and haven't had a chance to update my podcast. If you missed my last Thursday's Mixset for World Wide Dance Music Nation  live stream website, you can download/listen to it right here on this episode. There are a lot of awesome tracks presented in this mixset and you don't want to miss out. I hope you like it. Let me know by liking my facebook page or follow me here at podomatic.com.

Thank you again for listening.

Dj Arity Worldwide Dance Music Nation Playlist for 04/12/2012:

  • Lissat n Voltaxx - Wardance (Coqui Selection Remix)
  • Trape - Que Que (Club Mix)
  • Mr Jean Louis - Sensuelle (The Cube Guys Remix)
  • D.T. n Mic-Line ft Toby Orme - Electronic Love (The Cube Guys Remix)
  • John Acquaviva n DJ Tonio - Da Daddy (Original Mix)

  • Mirko Rinaldi - Start Again (Giulio P. Remix)

Enjoy!
